headline: Apartments.com Releases Multifamily Rent Growth Report for November 2025
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., December 08, 2025--Today Apartments.com, an industry-leading online marketplace of CoStar Group (NASDAQ: CSGP), published its latest report on multifamily rent trends for November 2025.

headline: 2 Nasdaq 100 Stocks to Own for Decades and 1 We Turn Down
summary: The Nasdaq 100 (^NDX) is home to some of the biggest success stories in tech and growth investing. However, certain stocks in the index face challenges like profitability concerns, rising costs, or shifts in market trends.
